    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Confirmed diagnosis of melanoma and BRAFV600

          -  Signed Informed Consent Form

          -  Unresectable phase III or phase IV melanoma

